abstract_ssm: The Elena Humphreys Riot Grrrl Collection consists of material personally collected by Humphreys while she was involved in the Riot Grrrl movement in the 1990s, as well as material generated by and related to Riot Grrrl NYC's activities including zine-making and distribution, activism, and events.
